parameters: Aren't you going to read it?
I-I'll read it now. Don't rush me too much.

The demon king who became human returned to town
to search for a spouse.

You probably didn't think it would be easy to
find, but I'll walk around hoping to find even a
small clue.

However, contrary to the king's thoughts, a spouse
was found immediately.

It wasn't just the king who was searching, but
the spouse as well.

Although the husband was surprised and ran away,
their love for the king remains unchanged.

Apologizing, they tried again and searched for a
spouse.
And so, the two of them reconciled.
However, there is one unresolved problem.

The children were entrusted to an orphanage, but
they were not there when the couple visited.

They continued to search afterwards, but in the
end, they couldn't find anything.
Well, because it's something that wrote the truth.
Could it be that the child in this book...?
The real Leviathan is my mother.
I am the half-demon king and human.

I thought it would be convenient to introduce
myself as a king, so I lied.

The magic my mother used to become human is called
inheritance magic.
It's a magic that passes power to one's child.

And then, when I was at the orphanage, I suddenly
gained the power of a king and became a complete
demon.

Because of that power, I couldn't stay at the
orphanage and ended up wandering from place to
place.

Because I thought I was abandoned, I never tried
to search for my parents.

However, at one point, I heard about this book and
wanted to know the truth.

I heard that the final volume was here, so I
infiltrated, but I never expected to end up like
this.

However, I can finally fulfill my purpose with
this.

Thanks to Leviathan, I was able to save Amelia
too.
But, I still can't believe it.

Leviathan is a half-demon and human, and moreover,
the true king of demons no longer exists.
I have truly inherited the power of Leviathan.

You can understand that by seeing magic. But there
are also clumsy aspects of being caught by
students.

T-That's because I was careless due to the
existence of magic that can turn back time.

After being caught, I slept for a few days and
waited for my magic power to recover, but it ended
up taking more than a week to return.

Since I only inherited a few magic spells, I
couldn't force myself to use them.

And...there's one more thing I want to ask you in
the end.

I need to replenish my magic power. I've used too
much.

I'm not doing anything bad, just give me a little
bit.

I'm telling you to have sex with me. Don't let
everyone hear it.

Don't misunderstand. I just want magic power,
that's all.

...It's fine. Even if I don't think it'll feel
that good for me.

Don't say such things. It's my first time, so be
gentle.
Tch... I wanted to try it.

Well, it's fine. Actually, I have plenty of magic
power.
